e-date=2015年7月31日|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150731022149/http://www.nytimes.com/2015/07/29/world/asia/escalator-death-in-china-sets-off-furor-online.html?_r=0|dead-url=no}}</ref>等，亦作出了报道。

